---
import ThemeLayout from '../layouts/ThemeLayout.astro';
---
<ThemeLayout page="services" heading="Mobile Friendly Websites">

  <section class="inner-page padd-section">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="row align-items-center mb-5" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 text-center mb-4 mb-md-0">
          <div class="svc-hero-icon">
            <i class="fa fa-tablet"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-10">
          <h3>Websites That Work on Every Device</h3>
          <p>Rayinfos Technologies designs and develops mobile-friendly websites that effectively showcase your products and services to target audiences on all smart phone platforms — Android, iPhone and Blackberry — with layouts, colours and navigation designed for mobile convenience.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-th-large"></i></div>
            <h5>Professional Layout</h5>
            <p>Clean, professional mobile layouts emphasising the most important features with only the required design factors.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-universal-access"></i></div>
            <h5>Accessibility &amp; Usability</h5>
            <p>Strategies to enhance website accessibility and usability, keeping layout, fonts and navigation convenient for mobile users.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-search"></i></div>
            <h5>SEO Friendly</h5>
            <p>SEO-friendly mobile layout and design from the ground up, with a result-oriented approach to mobile website marketing.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-bolt"></i></div>
            <h5>Fast Loading</h5>
            <p>Optimised features and graphics ensure quick downloading of the website on mobile phones without sacrificing visual quality.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-mobile"></i></div>
            <h5>Cross-platform Compatible</h5>
            <p>Better compatibility so the website functions correctly on all smart phone browsers, from Android to iOS and Blackberry.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-bullhorn"></i></div>
            <h5>Call to Action</h5>
            <p>Effectively customised call-to-action elements and mobile-friendly messaging to convert mobile visitors into customers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</ThemeLayout>
